			<div class="excerpt-container"><div class="excerpt"><em>The following is from Ariel Delgado Dixon's </em>Sourland<em>. Dixon was born and raised in Trenton, New Jersey. She is the author of the novels </em>Sourland<em> and </em>Don’t Say We Didn’t Warn You<em>. She lives in Western Massachusetts where she works in farming and teaches writing.</em></div></div>
